events.name: Career Fast-Track: Learn To Code & Get a Job as a Web Developer
events.description:
About This Event:
The web development industry is booming. If you are curious about a new career as a Web Developer, join us for a panel discussion about what day-to-day life looks like in this in-demand field. Explore how to launch a new career with in-demand skills in web development.

Bring your questions for our panel of Web Development leaders. They will give you insight into their roles, help you understand what is needed to get there, and, just maybe, inspire you to make a change.

Join us for insightful discussion, drinks, and community.

In this special edition Career Fast Track session, we will cover:
-The steps that you need to take to get into the Web Development industry.
-What a Web Developer does day-to-day, and what skills youâ€™ll need to be successful in the field.
-What you can expect to be paid throughout your career.
-Key areas of growth within the industry.
